Package com.camerontec.catalys.core.session.event

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ICatalysEventType
    This interface defines all the standard Catalys event type constants.
    ISessionStatusEventListener
    Session status events are occur whenever anything significant occurs on a Session.
    ISessionStatusListener
    This is a listener to Session status events once they have been split out into method calls.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActiveStatusEvent
    Event fired when a Session manager's active status changes.
    BlockedStatusEvent
    Event fired when a Session manager's blocked status changes.
    ConfigurationChangeEvent
    Event fired when the configuration changes.
    ConnectionPointEvent
    Base class for events relating to connection points.
    DeletedConnectionPointEvent
    Event fired when an IConnectionPoint is deleted.
    DisconnectRequestedEvent
    Event fired when a session disconnect is requested.
    ExceptionThrownEvent
    Event fired when a Catalys exception is thrown.
    FixMessageEvent
    Base class of message related events.
    InMessageDecryptedEvent
    Event fired when an input message has been decrypted.
    InMessageReceivedEvent
    Fired when a raw message is first received.
    LoggedOnStatusEvent
    Event fired when the logged on status of a session changes.
    NewConnectionPointEvent
    Event fired when a new IConnectionPoint is detected.
    NewSessionEvent
    Event fired when a new Session is created.
    NewSessionManagerEvent
    Event fired when a new SessionManager is created.
    OutMessageSendEvent
    Event fired when a message is about to be sent.
    ResendStatusEvent
    Event fired when the resending status of a Session changes.
    ResetEvent
    Event fired when a Session's sequence numbers are reset.
    SessionLifeCycleEvent
    This is the base class for events relating to a session's life cycle.
    SessionListenerSelector
    This ISelector implementation will only select CameronEvent objects with certain event types.
    SessionStatusEventRouter
    Takes session status events and calls associated methods on an ISessionStatusListener object.
    UpdatedMessageSeqNumEvent
    Event fired when a message sequence number is updated.
